## 🎨 Styling Guidelines

### Permission State Colors
```css
/* Plan colors */
.plan-starter { @apply bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 border-gray-300; }
.plan-business { @apply bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 border-blue-300; }
.plan-professional { @apply bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 border-purple-300; }

/* Usage indicators */
.usage-safe { @apply text-green-600 bg-green-50; }
.usage-warning { @apply text-yellow-600 bg-yellow-50; }
.usage-danger { @apply text-red-600 bg-red-50; }

/* Feature gates */
.feature-locked { @apply opacity-50 pointer-events-none; }
.feature-available { @apply opacity-100; }
```

